---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Surgery — Program Requirements" description="RACS SET surgical training program and assessment requirements.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Program Requirements</h1>
    <p>Surgery — RACS SET Program</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Workplace-Based Assessments (WBAs)</h2>
    <p>Ongoing throughout training. Assessments include:</p>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>Mid-Term and End of Term reports</li>
      <li>Case Based Discussions (CBD)</li>
      <li>Direct Observation of Procedural Skills (DOPS)</li>
      <li>Entrustable Professional Activities (EPAs)</li>
      <li>Procedure Based Activities (PBAs)</li>
      <li>Mini Clinical Examination (Mini-CEX)</li>
      <li>Logbooks — operative case records throughout training</li>
      <li>Tutorials</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Progression</h2>
    <p>Trainees progress through training terms with supervisor oversight. Mid-term and end-of-term reports determine progression. Struggling trainees are supported through formal processes before decisions on continuation are made.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
